						<div class="postbody">All nametables use the same address. If you draw one, switch the other, draw it, and switch back, yes it's possible. BUT, the PPU only sees 1KB of RAM at any point, so it will NOT know there's 2KB. It's a technical thing. I' suggest you learn more about normal mirroring and then more on address lines, as it all works together.</div>

